{"tid":329360,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]果年同miss 開始左","createTime":"2017-07-20T10:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T03:49:25.000Z","uid":129925,"like":55,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db4db09480ac2b2a9278bddc5500995ba9543bdf","tid":329360,"uid":129925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:02:07.000Z","msg":"真人真事  <br />\n想記低自己果幾個月既事 <br />\n小弟打文比較慢  同真係冇圖  <br />\n件事係2010年前發生   <br />\n<br />\n第一次見到你 其實我先中2 <br />\n果陣我仲係唔讀書 掛住玩既死靚仔 <br />\n你係第一年教書  好青春  好純<br />\n但唔識化妝 同少少老土 <br />\n其實中2 果陣冇咩感情產生到  <br />\n只係交代番個時間"},{"pid":"a585a65b9a227af5bef75dcbd04f9c4e941e0018","tid":329360,"uid":115810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"留名，支持。"},{"pid":"3ddb7efcd611a469a667d2e2aef19400470cb236","tid":329360,"uid":100356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a99341d4e5946911930a6047d4998a8bf70dcac6","tid":329360,"uid":35192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"11a94ec545c7cf0711b50ffcbf10ba10acbb31aa","tid":329360,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"下篇文要等幾耐"},{"pid":"042a12c465151f9da18689d1abc133b36c8ceaa2","tid":329360,"uid":129925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"講番先 miss 係教英文 <br />\n中2果陣  我成績唔好又個人壞壞地 <br />\n果陣係miss 心中 同其他老師心中都係搞事果堆<br />\n仲被編左入英文差果一班  係小班教學 20人到 <br />\n果陣又遲交功課 又做到成pat 屎咁  <br />\n佢都記得我係一個唔讀書學生  <br />\n果陣都覺得幾靚女 但冇諗過要一齊 有咩會發生 <br />\n仲覺得佢好煩"},{"pid":"752eb67d4f2f7340cbe31a31b741b31401f67600","tid":329360,"uid":13465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"正 留名"},{"pid":"b8854d95a2528a50d1ff8cb29f4edcd6a551afeb","tid":329360,"uid":14576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"劉明"},{"pid":"c5df7f013b52d9